                     <interp inst="t18221204-114-person1059" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I sent my daughter Ann to the gilders in Attfield-street, for these watch-works; three gentlemen brought the prisoner and her to me, she then had the bag in her hand, the gentlemen said, in the prisoner's presence,</p>
               <p>"We have brought the thief that stole the watch," he did not deny it. I gave him in charge, he acknowledged taking it, but said he did not mean to keep it.</p>
